# 创建一个画布
fig=plt.figure(figsize=(4,2),   # 横向：纵向
              dpi=500)     # 图像更清晰
# 准备数据
X=np.linspace(-5,5)
ycos=np.cos(X)
ysin=np.sin(X)
# plt.plot(X,ycos,
#         linestyle='',
#         linewidth=1,
#         color='#1976d2',
#         marker='^')   # 查颜色编码
plt.plot(X,ycos,'-*b',
        X,ysin,'--.k')
plt.show()

fig1=plt.figure(figsize=(4,2),dpi=200)

plt.title('正弦余弦图',fontsize=14,color='b',loc='center')   #标题
plt.legend()      # 把标记呈现出来变成图例
plt.xlabel('自变量',fontsize=10,color='k',loc='right')
plt.ylabel('应变量',fontsize=10,color='k',loc='center')
# plt.xticks([0,0.5,1],[0,0.5,1])    # 标记刻度信息

plt.grid(linestyle='-.',
         linewidth=1,
         color='#616161',
         alpha=0.1)
plt.text(0,1,
        'sin波峰',
        horizontalalignment='center',
        verticalalignment='top')

yd=5*np.cos(zd)

Z=np.sin(X)+np.cos(Y)

#柱状图的数据需要特别处理一下
Xh=X.flatten()
Yh=Y.flatten()
Zh=Z.flatten()

XX=np.arange(-5,5,0.1)
YY=np.arange(-5,5,0.1)
X,Y=np.meshgrid(XX,YY)  # 有函数的时候非常常用
Z=np.sin(X)+np.cos(Y)
fig=plt.figure()
ax3=fig.add_subplot(111,projection='3d')#画子图
ax3.plot_surface(X,Y,Z,rstride=1,cstride=1,cmap='gray')#绘制平面
plt.show()
In [32]:
from matplotlib import cm
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
 
fig = plt.figure()#显示绘图窗口
ax = fig.add_subplot(projection = '3d')#绘图窗口设置
[x, t] = np.meshgrid(np.array(range(25))/24.0, np.arange(0, 575.5, 0.5)/575*17*np.pi-2*np.pi)
p = (np.pi/2)*np.exp(-t/(8*np.pi))
u = 1-(1-np.mod(3.6*t, 2*np.pi)/np.pi)**4/2
y = 2*(x**2-x)**2*np.sin(p)
r = u*(x*np.sin(p)+y*np.cos(p))
surf = ax.plot_surface(r*np.cos(t), r*np.sin(t), u*(x*np.cos(p)-y*np.sin(p)), rstride=1,
    cstride=1,cmap=cm.Reds_r,linewidth = 0, antialiased = True)#根据参数绘图
 
#自己设置文字内夸和显示设置
ax.text(-0.3,0,1.2,'LOVE', color='red')
plt.axis('off')
plt.show()
